# Vision Report™ / DreamScape (Supabase Edge Function secrets — Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets)
# Also used locally if you shell-invoke functions with `supabase secrets`.
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=Socialutely <vision@your-verified-domain.com>
# VISION_REPORT_CTA_URL=https://your-site.com/checkout-or-calendar
# VAPI_DREAMSCAPE_ASSISTANT_ID=0693b0d9-6e89-436f-bdbd-9fe25cc1bf3c
